metadata.title: Applauding the Data Fellowship Award Winners: Champions of Innovation! - Sunway College Kathmandu
content.main_content: Applauding the Data Fellowship Award Winners: Champions of Innovation! We are thrilled to announce the prestigious Data Fellowship Award winners, marking a significant step forward in their quest to conquer the ever-evolving frontiers of Data Science and Artificial Intelligence. Through unwavering dedication and a pursuit of excellence, these remarkable individuals are paving the way for a future driven by data-driven ingenuity. Our hearts swell with pride every day, witnessing their commitment and progress. To all the winners, we offer our heartfelt congratulations once again! A special thank you also goes to all participants for their unwavering consistency and insatiable thirst for knowledge. Your enthusiasm fuels our passion, and we are incredibly grateful for your presence on this journey. Let this be a moment of inspiration for all. The world of data beckons, and with dedication and the right guidance, anyone can become a champion of innovation. Onward to even greater achievements! metadata.title: 7 Days Free Digital Marketing  Data Science Bootcamp - Sunway College Kathmandu
content.main_content: 7 Days Free Digital Marketing  Data Science Bootcamp Sunway College has been regularly organizing Free Bootcamp that covers various topics on Digital Marketing and Data Science. The Bootcamp features topic field experts and the overall workshops help its students clear the path for their digital marketing or data science journey. At every Bootcamp, 7-8 topics are covered related to digital marketing and data science, and every day only one topic is focused on. The 7-day Bootcamp usually covers topics on Digital Marketing Frameworks, Content Writing, Social Media Marketing, Graphic Designing, Personal Branding, SEO, Pinterest, and the Scope of Data Science in Nepal. Sunway College has successfully completed around 4 Bootcamps and regularly conducts them. metadata.title: Multimedia Training by Verside Production - Sunway College Kathmandu
content.main_content: Multimedia Training by Verside Production Sunway college organized multimedia and videography training for 1st and 6th-semester students. The training included guidance and tips on videography and the overall multimedia field. The training started on 20th June 2022. Sunway IT and Research Club organized and managed the training event successfully and the training was full of value and experience. metadata.title: Sunwayian Spotlight: Inspiring Alumni Talk Recap with Mr. Kiran Prajapati Data Engineer - Sunway College Kathmandu
content.main_content: Sunwayian Spotlight: Inspiring Alumni Talk Recap with Mr. Kiran Prajapati Data Engineer Sunway College Kathmandu proudly hosted an Experience Sharing Session on February 4th, 2024, featuring our esteemed alumnus, Mr. Kiran Prajapati, a successful Data Engineer at Nankai Electric Railway Co. Ltd. in Osaka, Japan. This event was a fantastic opportunity for our current students and aspiring professionals to gain valuable insights into the exciting world of Data Science and Artificial Intelligence. Mr. Prajapati, through his engaging presentation and interactive session, shared his journey from being a Sunwayian to carving a successful career path in the data field. He emphasized the importance of: Building a strong foundation: He highlighted the crucial role his education at Sunway College Kathmandu played in equipping him with the necessary skills and knowledge. Embracing continuous learning: He stressed the importance of staying updated with the ever-evolving nature of Data Science and AI technologies. Developing key skills: He identified critical skills like problem-solving, analytical thinking, and communication as essential for success in this field. Networking and building connections: He shared the importance of networking with industry professionals and building meaningful connections. Sunway College Kathmandu is incredibly proud of Mr. Prajapatis accomplishments and deeply appreciative of him taking the time to share his experiences and inspire our current students. We are confident that his insights will motivate them to excel in their academic journey and future careers. Missed the event? Stay tuned for upcoming alumni sessions and career-oriented workshops organized by Sunway College Kathmandu! metadata.title: Data Science with Python - Sunway College Kathmandu
content.main_content: Data Science with Python Data Science is Python is a short course offered at Sunway College Kathmandu in partnership with NCC, UK. Entry Requirement: Willingness to invest a minimum of 15 hours per week Programming Basics in QBasicCC or similar is preferable No particular education requirement The selection of the candidate is subject to a comprehensive test to analyze their knowledge level Basic Course2 months Python 1: Introduction to Python Introduction to programming and Python Setting up Python environment IDEs, text editors, online interpreters Writing and running your first Python program Variables, data types, and basic operations Comments and code structure 2: Control Structures Conditional statements if, else, elif Comparison operators and boolean logic Loops for and while Break and continue statements Practical exercises and mini-projects 3: Functions and Modules Defining and calling functions Parameters and return values Scope and lifetime of variables Introduction to built-in functions and modules Creating and importing custom modules 4: Data Structures Lists, tuples, and sets Accessing and manipulating elements List comprehensions Dictionaries and key-value pairs Practical exercises involving data structures 5: Exception Handling in Python Understanding exceptions in Python Importance of exception handling Types of exceptions and their meaning try-except blocks to handle exceptions Catching specific exceptions Handling multiple exceptions Using the try-except-else-finally blocks Raising Exceptions 6: File Handling Reading from and writing to files Working with text and binary files Exception handling try, except, finally CSV and JSON file formats Practical file processing examples 7: Object-Oriented Programming OOP Introduction to OOP concepts Classes and objects Attributes and methods Encapsulation, inheritance, and polymorphism Creating and using classes in Python 8: Debugging and Testing Debugging techniques and tools Common errors and how to fix them Writing and running unit tests Using assertions for testing Best practices for writing maintainable code Data Analysis 1.Introduction to Data Analysis with Python Overview of data analysis and its importance Introduction to key libraries: NumPy, pandas, and matplotlib Loading and exploring datasets using pandas Basic data exploration and summary statistics Join Our Workshop Post navigation Previous: Sunwayian Spotlight: Inspiring Alumni Talk Recap with metadata.title: 7 Days Free Digital Marketing  Data Science Bootcamp - Sunway College Kathmandu
content.main_content: 7 Days Free Digital Marketing  Data Science Bootcamp Sunway College has been regularly organizing Free Bootcamp that covers various topics on Digital Marketing and Data Science. The Bootcamp features topic field experts and the overall workshops help its students clear the path for their digital marketing or data science journey. At every Bootcamp, 7-8 topics are covered related to digital marketing and data science, and every day only one topic is focused on. The 7-day Bootcamp usually covers topics on Digital Marketing Frameworks, Content Writing, Social Media Marketing, Graphic Designing, Personal Branding, SEO, Pinterest, and the Scope of Data Science in Nepal. Sunway College has successfully completed around 4 Bootcamps and regularly conducts them. metadata.title: Applauding the Data Fellowship Award Winners: Champions of Innovation! - Sunway College Kathmandu
content.main_content: Applauding the Data Fellowship Award Winners: Champions of Innovation! We are thrilled to announce the prestigious Data Fellowship Award winners, marking a significant step forward in their quest to conquer the ever-evolving frontiers of Data Science and Artificial Intelligence. Through unwavering dedication and a pursuit of excellence, these remarkable individuals are paving the way for a future driven by data-driven ingenuity. Our hearts swell with pride every day, witnessing their commitment and progress. To all the winners, we offer our heartfelt congratulations once again! A special thank you also goes to all participants for their unwavering consistency and insatiable thirst for knowledge. Your enthusiasm fuels our passion, and we are incredibly grateful for your presence on this journey. Let this be a moment of inspiration for all. The world of data beckons, and with dedication and the right guidance, anyone can become a champion of innovation. Onward to even greater achievements!
